com.dp16.dynamicrunninginghent.Persistence

Class ServerStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dp16.dynamicrunninginghent.Persistence.ServerStorage

  • public class ServerStorage
extends java.lang.Object
    Storage component that takes care of the server side storage on the MongoDB database. Before calling any of the methods that interact with the database, connect() should be called. Otherwise the methods will return failures. Likewise, disconnect() should be called to clean up resources. Created by Nick on 9-4-2017.
